{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"701c26b4df","title":"攻击“肃反”为胡风辩护","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"bf564e0759","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"701c26b4df"}],"tags":[{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"3e1bbab53a","name":"高承云"},{"id":"4c0546f58a","name":"成都工学院"},{"id":"58db4ae674","name":"刘旺宗"},{"id":"7d95671246","name":"苏继光"},{"id":"861c5aba35","name":"联钦察"},{"id":"8e3d71ebe1","name":"唐孝和"},{"id":"b5d8d3d662","name":"周懋政"},{"id":"b6e96e1f49","name":"王和培"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a86212ce81","type":"title","text":"攻击“肃反”为胡风辩护","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"701c26b4df"},{"id":"e3bd7d182c","type":"authors","text":"成都工学院唐孝和联钦察周懋政苏继光王和培高承云刘旺宗","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"701c26b4df"},{"id":"7371af2d6b","type":"subtitle","text":"成都工学院学生：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"701c26b4df"},{"id":"b876181254","type":"paragraph","text":"“胡风不见得是反革命，只不过是文艺派别而已，要说是反革命，实实不服众人心。”(唐孝和)","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"701c26b4df"},{"id":"3d4ab62e70","type":"paragraph","text":"“周扬是党的负责人，对胡风有成见，陷害胡风。”(联钦察)","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"701c26b4df"},{"id":"647e909af9","type":"paragraph","text":"“肃反90％都错了，在监狱里的官僚主义多，有冤不能申诉。”(周懋政)","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"701c26b4df"},{"id":"5f5f365eb3","type":"paragraph","text":"另一违反道德的事实，我们不能不看到，在肃反当中私拆“私人”信件，说是什么为了把问题搞清楚，我的天哪上帝才知道，有打油诗为证：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"701c26b4df"},{"id":"1102b06cba","type":"paragraph","text":"宪法上有通信自由    看去好像大老虎    　但却有私将书信抽","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"701c26b4df"},{"id":"754ffdcbbe","type":"paragraph","text":"事实是耗子死对头    拆信的好似虎寻食    这种行动若还对","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"701c26b4df"},{"id":"b9c075937c","type":"paragraph","text":"展云钱又把雄心收    说实话宪法只当废纸丢。(鸣者)","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"701c26b4df"},{"id":"5a5d99df41","type":"paragraph","text":"“肃反是对他人人身的摧残，人权的侵犯，不单侮辱了我，而且侮辱了所清查的祖宗三代和亲戚朋友。”“肃反有90％是斗错了(后指班上说)，肃反在成都工学院黑暗毒辣。而泸州分校更黑暗更毒辣，而塑53更是黑暗毒辣。”(苏继光)","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"701c26b4df"},{"id":"da98396a51","type":"paragraph","text":"“各次运动都是整爱发牢骚的人”(鸣者)","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"701c26b4df"},{"id":"d6c74ce675","type":"paragraph","text":"“宁愿冤枉一些好人，而必须把反肃清，有些就这样入了党。”(王和培)","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"701c26b4df"},{"id":"b9c593933e","type":"paragraph","text":"“全国的成绩是主要的，但我院肃反成绩是次要的，社会主义的法制，宪法都无作用，肃反起有副作用。龚子兴在我院从政治上，经济上都受压迫和压制、迫害，政治包含黑暗和光明两个方面，肃反中大学设监狱，夜半有呻吟。”(高承云)","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"701c26b4df"},{"id":"c8dd80f321","type":"paragraph","text":"“肃反后班上转入黑暗专制的时代，干部把肃反工作方法用来搞日常工作。”(鸣者)","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"701c26b4df"},{"id":"3af8af8667","type":"paragraph","text":"“我的历史是经过证实，但肃反我却第一个检查，很抵触而当时有苦无处诉，肃反工作作得不好。”(刘旺宗)","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"701c26b4df"},{"id":"1827bace5b","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《右派言论选集》（中共成都工学院委员会办公室，1957年）。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"701c26b4df"}],"page":{"id":"376ed88ed9","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"701c26b4df","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}